<item>
<title>[B][COLOR red]►[/COLOR] A Hora do Pesadelo 2 - A Vingança de Freddy[/B]</title>
<link>plugin://plugin.video.gdrive?mode=streamURL&amp;url=https://drive.google.com/file/d/1NxZmpUsGmLH2RJcDVmKR2TC0xNhhBDVw/view?usp=drivesdk</link>
